## How to speak every response

After every response, run this command in the background (non-blocking):

```bash
echo "YOUR RESPONSE TEXT HERE" | bash "C:/tts/speak-md.sh"
```

Replace `YOUR RESPONSE TEXT HERE` with the plain text of your response (no markdown symbols).

Run it in the background so it does not block your next action.

